Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:10.14,1080P思源-7,,0,0,0,,英文字幕:\h官方\N翻译: 谷歌翻译\N校对 润色 压制:\hBolshevik0
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:23.40,1080P思源-7,,0,0,0,,吐槽:\h官方玩梗最为致命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:30.10,1080P思源-7,,0,0,0,,吐槽:\h我闻到了一股批判DCS的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:10.14,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Hello everyone, my name is Kirill Yudintsev, I am the Creative Director of Gaijin Entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.14,0:00:12.70,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Today I'll be answering a number of your questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:13.88,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,A hot question.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:18.66,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,A lot of people are asking about the P-47 and its performance in Random battles,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.94,0:00:23.14,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,they ask if we are going to do something or change something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.58,0:00:28.40,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,First of all, we've just adjusted its BR, it will be a bit higher now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.12,0:00:37.84,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Then we'll work with the statistics, will see why and how it affects the outcomes in Random Battles, and then
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.84,0:00:42.40,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,depending on what we see, we might introduce further changes in the nearest future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.96,0:00:45.60,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Thank you for writing about things that concern you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:48.80,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,It's very important for us as it allows us to improve the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.80,0:00:51.40,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Many players ask about new game modes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.52,0:01:00.20,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,We actually organize a lot of different events with different rules
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:02.94,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,that deviate from what you see in Random Battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.90,0:01:12.58,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,The thing is that it's rather difficult to introduce new game modes in Random Battles,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.58,0:01:15.50,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,because we want them to be fair and balanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:19.40,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,This makes it quite challenging. Everything should be balanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.62,0:01:21.60,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,If we want the changes to be balanced,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:25.11,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,to make fair game modes, especially the asymmetric ones
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.31,0:01:29.00,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,that a lot of players want if we want it to be engaging and fair,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.20,0:01:32.50,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,it's much much more difficult than to make a separate event
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.50,0:01:38.04,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,that inherently has limitations like what kind of vehicles are allowed, how many players are in etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.34,0:01:43.82,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,That's why, first of all, do participate in our events! Right now it's Chronicles, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:46.74,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of interesting mechanics out there for you to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.26,0:01:50.26,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Apart from that, we are currently testing World War.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.72,0:01:56.24,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,This gamemode has a lot of new mechanics such as convoy and escort missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.24,0:02:02.46,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,These are missions of a completely new type, they are asymmetric, it's all very engaging and historical.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.46,0:02:06.46,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Well, it's much closer to what most real combat missions were,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.46,0:02:09.65,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,than the balanced skirmishes of two even sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:12.40,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,These feel more like combat scenarios.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.44,0:02:21.48,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,That's why I strongly suggest that you should try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:23.76,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Sign up for it, leave your feedback.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.76,0:02:28.52,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,We never test new game modes and new mechanics in Random Battles, we don't want to break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:31.40,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,We do it in our events or during tournaments
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:35.77,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,or, like now, in World War which is a completely new level altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:42.08,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Leave your feedback, maybe some of these mechanics will make it to Random Battles as well. We will see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.82,0:02:52.46,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Many people ask about Italian armour, a lot of players already own Italian premiums and aircraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:55.84,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,There are already Italian tanks in-game, two premium machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:03:00.56,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,A huge thanks to all who buy them, support our game and leave their feedback.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:07.78,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,We're already working on a full size ground tech tree for Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.78,0:03:10.02,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,We'll do our best to release it this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:13.37,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Maybe some tanks will appear in the game even earlier than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.74,0:03:17.62,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Creating the Italian ground tech tree is a very challenging process.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:23.40,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,We do love pizza and pasta, but it doesn't make it easier to find data on all those vehicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:30.24,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Many players are concerned about the role the M1 Abrams has in Random Battles,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:34.40,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,where it performs pretty well, mostly thanks to its excellent survivability.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.54,0:03:42.44,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,We've only implemented the feature the Abrams has in real life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:46.84,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,that it has a chance of surviving a fire in the ammunition storage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:50.14,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,In our game it works even better than in real life though,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:56.28,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,because in reality there was always a chance that the engine transmission compartment would catch fire as well
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:03:59.34,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,and to prevent that you had to rotate the turret.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:04.26,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,It's a fairly lengthy process, during which the tank is obviously unable to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:11.34,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,In the end the fire disables the vehicle anyway, and the crew, as a general rule, abandons it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:16.96,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,We plan to make it as realistic as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:22.66,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,If your ammo rack is on fire, you'll have to turn your turret away from the engine transmission compartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.66,0:04:23.92,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,That's the first thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.48,0:04:32.24,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,{\fs47}The second is that right now the piece of armour that separates the rack and the fighting compartment is way too sturdy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:36.14,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,making the tank practically invincible to the attacks from the rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:40.66,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,It's not the way it works in real life, so we'll be working on that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:46.12,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, if your rack catches fire, we'll make it impossible for a reload to finish. We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:48.48,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Maybe that will be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:54.30,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Because right now it's way tougher than in real life, and tougher than its opponents in the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:05.38,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,After we introduced new top tanks for a number of countries in the latest patch,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:11.22,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,many of you started to question the competitiveness of Japan, France and Germany at high ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.18,0:05:21.76,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,In one of the upcoming big updates we plan to introduce new vehicles for France.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:23.98,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Japan is in for a treat as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:26.54,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Maybe Germans will get a production Leopard 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.78,0:05:29.60,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,So they will get more powerful vehicles as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:43.88,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,By the way, the info about these plans was already shown on our website.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:46.88,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,As well as a lot of other exciting pieces of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:48.96,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Check out the news on our website right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.46,0:05:52.24,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,As a kind of a follow-up to the last Q&A session,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:58.40,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,a lot of players write that the 6th rank and top-tier aircraft aren't that difficult to implement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:04.64,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,That the early self-guided and guided missiles weren't that effective and won't change the flow of a match,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:08.70,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,that it's a kind of a nice thing to have that doesn't change everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:12.60,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,doesn't make WT in a new game that is completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:27.04,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,And all of that makes sense but you have to understand that if we introduce just the F-100 and the MiG-19
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:30.10,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,it will make WT into a game about duels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:32.98,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,And our game is very different from that after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:37.28,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,There are more than two nations, we have bombers and other types of aircraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:45.12,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,That might look fairly easy. And it actually is, to implement two aircraft that can fight each other on even terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:48.71,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,But we need to make it interesting for all countries,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:52.25,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,to make it balanced, to make it possible for bombers to play with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:57.00,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Because guided missiles or heat seekers weren't that effective against fighter aircraft,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:59.98,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,but were much more effective against bomber aircraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.52,0:07:18.16,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,This might even out the field with top-tier bombers, but it will change the game in a lot of ways nevertheless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:23.80,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,All in all, WT isn't just about two aircraft, isn't just about duels.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:28.43,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,That's why it's a lot of work, and we want it to be, as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:32.14,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,A whole new level for both aviation and gameplay,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:37.14,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,not just an attention grabber in the form of two supersonic jets and their missiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:43.82,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,That's why that requires a bit more in terms of our effort, with a lot of tests and brainstorming involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:51.05,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Thanks for watching this episode of our developer Q&A,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:54.00,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,thanks for watching the previous one and writing your questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.06,0:07:59.28,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Leave questions and feedback, we read it all, it's all very educational and exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:02.08,1080P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Leave likes and subscribe to the channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:10.14,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,大家好 我是Kirill Yudintsev 我是Gaijin娱乐公司的创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.14,0:00:12.70,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,今天我会回答你们的一些问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:13.88,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,一个热门的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:18.66,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,很多人都在问随机战斗中的P-47以及它的性能问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.94,0:00:23.14,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,他们问我们是否要做什么或者改什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.58,0:00:28.40,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,首先 我们调高了它的权重
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.12,0:00:37.84,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,然后 我们将根据统计数据 了解它对随机战斗结果的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.84,0:00:42.40,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,然后 根据这些结果 再进行进一步的改变
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.96,0:00:45.60,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,谢谢你写下你所关心的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:48.80,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,这对我们非常重要 因为它可以让我们改进游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.80,0:00:51.40,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,许多玩家询问新的游戏模式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.52,0:01:00.20,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,我们实际上组织了许多不同玩法的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:02.94,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,这些不同于随机战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.90,0:01:12.58,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,事实上在随机战斗中引入新的游戏模式相当困难
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.58,0:01:15.50,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,因为我们希望新模式足够公平和平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:19.40,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,这件事做起来不那么容易 颇具挑战性 其中的一切都应该平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.62,0:01:21.60,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,如果我们希望这些变化是平衡的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:25.11,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,制定公平的游戏模式 尤其是不对称的游戏模式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.31,0:01:29.00,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,正如许多玩家所想的那样 如果我们让它变得有趣又公平
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.20,0:01:32.50,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,要比做出一个独立的活动困难很多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.50,0:01:38.04,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,从对战本质上就限制了很多 譬如允许使用哪些载具 有多少玩家等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.34,0:01:43.82,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,所以的话 请先参加我们组织的活动 譬如现在的二战编年史
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:46.74,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,活动中有很多有趣的机制让你去尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.26,0:01:50.26,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,除此之外 我们正在测试世界大战模式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.72,0:01:56.24,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,这个游戏模式有很多新的机制 譬如护航和护航任务
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.24,0:02:02.46,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,这些全新类型的任务 既不对称又非常具有吸引力和历史性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.46,0:02:06.46,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,它更接近大多数真实战斗任务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.46,0:02:09.65,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,而不是双方均衡的小规模冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:12.40,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,这些感觉更像是战场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.44,0:02:21.48,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,这就是我强烈建议你尝试它的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:23.76,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,注册并留下你的反馈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.76,0:02:28.52,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,我们不想打破以往的规矩 就是不在随机战斗中测试新的游戏模式和新机制
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:31.40,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,而是在活动和竞技场中进行测试
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:35.77,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,或者像现在这样 完全在一个新的模式世界大战中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:42.08,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,留下你的反馈意见 也许一些新机制会出现在随机战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.82,0:02:52.46,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,很多人在问意大利陆战的事情 很多玩家已经拥有意大利的金币载具和飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:55.84,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,游戏中已经有两辆意大利金币载具
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:03:00.56,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,非常感谢所有购买它们来支持我们的游戏并反馈意见的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:07.78,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,我们已经在做意大利的完整陆战科技树
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.78,0:03:10.02,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,我们尽量在年内发布它
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:13.37,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,有些坦克也许会比这更早地出现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.74,0:03:17.62,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,创建意大利陆战科技树是一个非常具有挑战性的过程
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:23.40,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,我们确实喜欢披萨和意大利面 但这并不利于查找所有这些陆战载具的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:30.24,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,许多玩家都关心M1艾布拉姆斯在随机战斗中的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:34.40,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,它的表现相当不错 主要归功于其卓越的生存能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.54,0:03:42.44,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,我们只实现了Abrams在现实中的特点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:46.84,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,也就是有可能在弹药舱起火的状态下幸免于难
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:50.14,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,尽管如此 它在我们的游戏中的表现要比现实中的更好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:56.28,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,因为实际上发动机和传动系统总是有可能一起着火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:03:59.34,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,为了防止动力舱一起着火 你得转动炮塔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:04.26,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,这是一个相当漫长的过程 在这个过程中坦克显然无法战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:11.34,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,最后 火灾总是会使车辆无法使用 并且成员通常会放弃它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:16.96,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,我们计划让这些尽可能还原
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:22.66,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,如果你的弹药架着火 则你必须将炮塔从动力舱上方移开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.66,0:04:23.92,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,这是第一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.48,0:04:32.24,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,第二件事则是 现在把弹药架和战斗室隔开的那部分装甲太坚固了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:36.14,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,使坦克几乎可以无视来自炮塔后方的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:40.66,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,现实中并非如此 所以这点以后也会被改进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:46.12,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,如果你的弹药架着火了 也许就不能再装填弹药 我们拭目以待
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:48.48,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,也许这些改进就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:54.30,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,因为现在这样要比现实中的更强 也比它的对手更强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:05.38,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,在最新版本中为多个国家推出新的顶级坦克之后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:11.22,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,你们中的许多人开始质疑日本 法国和德国的顶级房水准
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.18,0:05:21.76,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,在即将到来的重大更新之一中 我们计划为法国推出新的陆战载具
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:23.98,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,同样还有日本
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:26.54,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,也许德系会得到一个豹2系列的坦克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.78,0:05:29.60,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,所以他们也会获得更为强大的车辆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:43.88,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,顺便说一句 在我们的网站上能找到关于这些计划的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:46.88,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,以及许多其他令人兴奋的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:48.96,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,请马上看看我们网站上的新闻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.46,0:05:52.24,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,作为上次问答部分的后续
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:58.40,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,很多玩家都说 6级和顶级飞机并不难实现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:04.64,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,早期的被动制导和主动制导导弹没有那么有效 也不会改变游戏的流程
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:08.70,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,没多大变化是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:12.60,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,这不会让战争雷霆变得完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:27.04,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,这些说的都有道理 但是你必须理解如果我们只推出F-100和米格-19
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:30.10,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,就会让战争雷霆成为一场关于决斗的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:32.98,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,毕竟我们的游戏与此截然不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:37.28,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,我们有两个以上的国家 以及轰炸机和其他类型的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:45.12,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,要实现两架可以相互对抗的飞机可能挺简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:48.71,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,但是我们需要加入所有国家的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:52.25,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,让整场游戏变得平衡 同时轰炸机也可以加入战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:57.00,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,由于制导导弹或红外导引头对战斗机不是很有效
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:59.98,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,但是对轰炸机来说效率要高得多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.52,0:07:18.16,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,这甚至超出了顶级轰炸机的领域 但是不管怎样 这会大幅改变游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:23.80,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,总而言之 战争雷霆不是关于两架飞机决斗的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:28.43,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,这就是为啥6级飞机的实现仍然比较困难 而且我们也想实现很多机制
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:32.14,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,对于空战和游戏玩法来说都是全新的层次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:37.14,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,不仅仅是吸引热度的两个超音速喷气式飞机和它们的导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:43.82,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,这就是我们需要更加努力的原因 这需要进行大量的测试和头脑风暴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:51.05,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,感谢观看我们这集开发者问答
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:54.00,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,同时感谢你们在看完前面那期之后的留言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.06,0:07:59.28,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,在油管的评论区留下问题和反馈 我们都会看一遍 这都是非常有教育意义和令人兴奋的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:02.08,1080P思源-2,,0,0,0,,到油管上点赞并订阅本频道
